{"tid":1294482,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"下次我覺得唔應該同上齊裝備嘅警察硬碰","createTime":"2019-07-07T19:16:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T04:09:32.000Z","uid":43785,"like":21,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"334c8fb7e82a0c46fb32cf8b0aefd79bbebb335c","tid":1294482,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T19:16:15.000Z","msg":"下次我覺得唔應該同上齊裝備嘅警察硬碰。<br />\n人哋上齊裝備幾十個盾， 個個有頭盔，你同人哋撞盾有乜嘢用。<br />\n<br />\n你地自己都知，贏唔到就應該要走。<br />\n大佬呀搞抗爭梗係想成功架啦。<br />\n<br />\n咁點樣先可以成功呀？ 咪就係唔好同啲有裝備同頭盔嘅警察對抗囉。 企喺人哋個盾面前畀人扑爆頭冇意思。走啦！<br />\n<br />\n香港人係咪成世都要做畀黑警扑爆頭嗰個？<br />\n係咪成世要做俾狗追嗰個？<br />\n面對惡法，面對黑警係咪成世要做認輸嗰個？<br />\n<br />\n你哋甘心嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我見到黑警亂咁打人，我好心痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n究竟香港人幾時先可以贏， 究竟有冇贏嘅方法？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n撐住呀，香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a797c2a965cbd17ec63c4d53ce4c6eec284adf38","tid":1294482,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T00:07:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"211e2f345df6d9fb497efef6d4698c8f700a3057","tid":1294482,"uid":180173,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T00:09:01.000Z","msg":"認同啊"},{"pid":"0d7f8aab6450e9d584589726222a84eaf1826ead","tid":1294482,"uid":147664,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T00:09:07.000Z","msg":"你係咪訓左無睇?<br />\n無人同狗硬碰<br />\n係撤緊佢地都照打人"},{"pid":"b7f7b37890cbea48d26a1d292b52a5334ef7561a","tid":1294482,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T00:10:26.000Z","msg":"又一個冇睇直播<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gi